FBIS4-21806 "jptot014__l94106" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 31 March 1994 WEST EUROPE CYPRUS Nicosia Paper Says PKK, Armenian `Terrorist' Base in Cyprus Nicosia Paper Says PKK, Armenian `Terrorist' Base in Cyprus Government Source Denies Claims on Camps NC3103200294 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network in Greek 1900 GMT 31 Mar 94 NC3103200294 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network Greek BFN [Excerpt] [passage omitted] A competent government source told CyBC this evening that the Turkish claims about the existence of camps for the training of Kurds in the free areas of Cyprus are absolutely unfounded. [passage omitted]
